# Agent automation (logpilot)

Follow **[`docs/agents/AUTOMATION.md`](../../docs/agents/AUTOMATION.md)** in addition to **[`docs/agents/MAINTAIN.md`](../../docs/agents/MAINTAIN.md)**.

## Before marking substantive work complete

1. Apply the **MAINTAIN** matrix for every change category you touched.
2. Run **`make check`** (or `PYTHON=.venv/bin/python make check` if needed).
3. For **cross-cutting** design (architecture, safety boundary, new connector policy), add **`docs/decisions/NNN_….md`** (see [`docs/decisions/README.md`](../../docs/decisions/README.md)).
4. For **roadmap / phase** changes, update **[`docs/plans/local-sysadmin-copilot-roadmap.md`](../../docs/plans/local-sysadmin-copilot-roadmap.md)** or the relevant plan under **`docs/plans/`**.

## Task size

Prefer **small, explicit tasks** (one concern) so checks and doc updates stay tractable.

## Optional for the human

Suggest **`make install-git-hooks`** once per clone so **`git push`** runs **`make check`** automatically (skip with `LOGPILOT_SKIP_HOOKS=1` if truly needed).
